PrecisAmendment to Part LXVIII of the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS which, for the purposes of the definition "foreign retirement arrangement" in subsection 248(1) of the Act, specifies that a prescribed plan or arrangement is one to which subsection 408(a), (b) or (h) of the U.S. Internal Revenue Code of 1986 applies.
